attachments.title: The Subaru Viziv-7 Is The Seven Seat SUV That Will Cement Subaru's Takeover Of America
attachments.text: America has an addiction: an addiction to buying Subarus. Over the past few years this great nation has been snatching up the Outbacks and the Foresters (and in the case of socially irresponsible people, the BRZs and the STIs) almost immediately after they roll off the assembly lines. But the people demand more: more seats, more space, more size. Subaru has finally answered the call.
